{"title_page": "Bheeshma (2020 film)", "text_new": "{{short description|2020 Indian film directed by Venky Kudumula}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Bheeshma \n| image          = Bheeshma Poster.jpeg\n| caption        = Theatrical release poster\n| director       = Venky Kudumula\n| producer       = Suryadevara Naga Vamsi\n| writer         = Venky Kudumula\n| screenplay     = Venky Kudumula\n| story          = Venky Kudumula\n| starring       = {{ubl|[[Nithiin]]|[[Rashmika Mandanna]]|[[Anant Nag]]|[[Vennela Kishore]]}}\n| music          = Mahati Swara Sagar\n| cinematography = Sai Sriram\n| editing        = Navin Nooli\n| studio         = Sithara Entertainments\n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{Film date|df=yes|2020|2|21|ref1=<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/haarikahassine/status/1192299051003179008?s=19|title=Here's the first glimpse of #Bheeshma. A very Happy Birthday to our Guiding Force & Wizard of Words, #Trivikram garu. #BheeshmaFirstGlimpse #HBDTrivikram Let's meet in theatres on 21st Feb 2020 @actor_nithiin @iamRashmika @VenkyKudumula @mahathi_sagar|first=Haarika & Hassine|last=Creations|date=6 November 2019}}</ref>}}\n| runtime        = 150 minutes\n| country        = India\n| language       = Telugu\n| budget         = 25 crores\n| boxoffice      = 35.6 crores\n}}\n'''''Bheeshma''''' is a 2020 Indian [[Telugu language|Telugu]]-language [[Romance film|romantic]] [[action comedy]] film directed by Venky Kudumula starring [[Nithiin]] and [[Rashmika Mandanna]] in lead roles. The film is produced by Suryadevara Nagavamsi under Sithara Entertainments with Mahati Swara Sagar handling music composition. The film was released on 21 February 2020  <ref>{{cite web|url=https://zeenews.india.com/regional/nithiin-reddy-and-rashmika-mandanna-launch-the-first-look-poster-of-bheeshma-2191336.html/amp|title=Nithiin Reddy and Rashmika Mandanna launch the first look poster of Bheeshma &#124; Regional News|website=zeenews.india.com|access-date=7 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107052102/https://zeenews.india.com/regional/nithiin-reddy-and-rashmika-mandanna-launch-the-first-look-poster-of-bheeshma-2191336.html/amp|archive-date=7 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== Cast ==\n{{Colbegin}}\n* [[Nithiin]] as Bheeshma Prasad \n* [[Rashmika Mandanna]] as Chaitra\n*[[Jisshu Sengupta]] as Raghavan\n* [[Anant Nag]] as Bheeshma<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/kannada/2019/nov/02/veteran-actor-anant-nag-returns-to-telugu-with-bheeshma--2055790.amp|title=Veteran actor Anant Nag returns to Telugu with Bheeshma - The New Indian Express|website=newindianexpress.com|access-date=7 November 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107052102/https://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/kannada/2019/nov/02/veteran-actor-anant-nag-returns-to-telugu-with-bheeshma--2055790.amp|archive-date=7 November 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*[[Vennela Kishore]] as Parimal\n*[[Sampath Raj]] as [[Assistant Commissioner|ACP]] Deva\n*[[Ajay (actor)|Ajay]] as Ajay Varma, Agricultural Minister\n*[[Naresh (actor)|Naresh]] as Anand Prasad, Bheeshma's father\n*[[Praveena]] as Bheeshma's mother\n*[[Bramhaji]] as JP\n*[[Mime Gopi]] as Purushottam\n*[[Kalyani Natarajan]] as Kalyani\n*[[Raghu Babu]] as Balram, Bheeshma's company employee\n*Darbha Appaji Ambarisha as Bheeshma's PA\n*Narra Srinivas as Raghavan's employee\n*[[Subhalekha Sudhakar]] as Ramaraju\n*[[Sathya (Telugu actor)|Sathya]] as Uber Driver\n*Shivakumar Ramachandravarapu as Shiva\n*Sudharshan as Employee\n*[[Hebah Patel]] (cameo appearance) as Sarah\n*[[Avantika Mishra]] (cameo appearance)\n{{Colend}}\n\n== Production ==\nThe film was announced on Nithiin's birthday by Rashmika Mandanna on social media platforms.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/iamRashmika/status/1111853316047147008?s=19|title=Happy happiest birthday to you @actor_nithiin siiirrrrrr have a great year ahead!! @VenkyKudumula @vamsi84 @SitharaEnts  this year is going to be so much fun. Let\u2019s show the fun we had while shooting on screens as well..can\u2019t wait! #Bheeshma #HappyBirthdayNithiinpic.twitter.com/GZp4tDGVTL|first=Rashmika|last=Mandanna|date=29 March 2019}}</ref> The pooja ceremony was held in early June 2019 and started principal photography.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/iamRashmika/status/1138789336843816962?s=19|title=All set! #Bheeshma Excited  can't wait for the shoot to start.  @actor_nithiin @VenkyKudumula @vamsi84 @SitharaEntspic.twitter.com/zC6P1qdoFx|first=Rashmika|last=Mandanna|date=12 June 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/SitharaEnts/status/1138423149937082369?s=19|title=Finally, For all @actor_nithiin fans who have been waiting for #Bheeshma, we have an exciting update.  Pooja ceremony of the movie will be held tomorrow and more details about the film will follow soon   @iamRashmika @venkykudumula @vamsi84pic.twitter.com/pipjR1W12i|first=Sithara|last=Entertainments|date=11 June 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Promotion and release ==\nThe film initially aimed at Christmas 2019, but was released on 21 February 2020.\n\nThe first look poster was released on Deepavali. The first teaser was released on [[Trivikram Srinivas]]'s birthday revealing the release date.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://telugu.samayam.com/telugu-movies/cinema-news/nithin-rashmika-mandanna-starrer-bheeshma-first-look-released/articleshow/71784842.cms|title=Bheeshma First Look: \u0c1a\u0c3f\u0c1f\u0c4d\u0c1f\u0c3f \u0c28\u0c21\u0c41\u0c2e\u0c41\u0c28\u0c3f \u0c12\u0c21\u0c3f\u0c38\u0c3f \u0c2a\u0c1f\u0c4d\u0c1f\u0c41.. \u2018\u0c2d\u0c40\u0c37\u0c4d\u0c2e\u2019 \u0c2b\u0c38\u0c4d\u0c1f\u0c4d\u200c\u0c32\u0c41\u0c15\u0c4d \u0c2a\u0c4b\u0c38\u0c4d\u0c1f\u0c30\u0c4d\u0c32\u0c41 \u0c05\u0c26\u0c41\u0c30\u0c4d\u0c38\u0c4d - nithin, rashmika mandanna starrer bheeshma first look released|website=Samayam Telugu|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107060834/https://telugu.samayam.com/telugu-movies/cinema-news/nithin-rashmika-mandanna-starrer-bheeshma-first-look-released/articleshow/71784842.cms|archive-date=7 November 2019|access-date=7 November 2019}}</ref> The official trailer of the film was released by Haarika & Hassine Creations on 17 February 2020.<ref>{{cite AV media|url=https://youtube.com/watch?v=8A9mJYprMl4|title=Bheeshma Theatrical Trailer - Nithiin, Rashmika Mandanna - Venky Kudumula|work=Haarika & Hassine Creations|publisher=YouTube|date=17 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Home Media ==\nThe movie was released on [[Netflix]] and [[Sun NXT]] on 25 April 2020 with English Subtitles.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://telugu.filmibeat.com/hero/nithiin-bheeshma-film-is-all-set-to-appear-on-ott-platforms-086215.html|title=\u0c28\u0c3f\u0c24\u0c3f\u0c28\u0c4d \u0c05\u0c2d\u0c3f\u0c2e\u0c3e\u0c28\u0c41\u0c32\u0c15\u0c41 \u0c17\u0c41\u0c21\u0c4d \u0c28\u0c4d\u0c2f\u0c42\u0c38\u0c4d.. \u0c2d\u0c40\u0c37\u0c4d\u0c2e \u0c2e\u0c33\u0c4d\u0c33\u0c40 \u0c35\u0c38\u0c4d\u0c24\u0c41\u0c28\u0c4d\u0c28\u0c3e\u0c21\u0c41!|last=Prashanth|first=Musti|date=2020-04-23|website=https://telugu.filmibeat.com|language=te|access-date=2020-04-24}}</ref>\n\n== Soundtrack ==\n{{Infobox album\n| name         = Bheeshma\n| type         = Soundtrack\n| artist       = Mahati Swara Sagar\n| cover        = \n| alt          = \n| released     = 2020\n| genre        = [[Feature Film Soundtrack]]\n| length       = 18:30\n| label        = [[Aditya Music]]\n| producer     = Mahati Swara Sagar\n| prev_title   = [[Nartanasala (2018 film)|Nartanasala]]\n| prev_year    = 2018\n| next_title   = \n| next_year    = \n}}\nThe music was composed by Mahati Swara Sagar.\n<br />{{Track listing\n| all_writing = \n| title7 = \n| lyrics1 = [[Sri Mani]]\n| extra1 = [[Anurag Kulkarni]]\n| total_length = 18:30\n| length10 = \n| title10 = \n| length9 = \n| title9 = \n| length8 = \n| title8 = \n| length7 = \n| length6 = \n| title1 = Singles Anthem\n| title6 = \n| length5 = 3:30\n| title5 = Hey Choosa\n| length4 = 3:41\n| title4 = Super Cute\n| length3 = 4:01\n| title3 = Sara Sari\n| length2 = 3:55\n| title2 = Whattey Beauty\n| length1 = 3:23\n| extra_column = Singers(s)\n| lyrics2 = Kasarla Shyam\n| extra2 = Dhanunjay, [[Amala Chebolu]]\n| extra3 = Anurag Kulkarni\n| lyrics3 = Sri Mani\n| extra4 = [[Nakash Aziz]]\n| lyrics4 = Sri Mani\n| lyrics5 = [[Krishna Chaitanya (lyricist)|Krishna Chaitanya]]\n| extra5 = Sanjana Kalmanje\n}}\n\n== Critical Response ==\nThe film opened to positive reviews from critics on the first day of its release with praise for its performances, comedy, songs and dance numbers.<ref>{{cite web|author=Feb 21, 2020 12:55 IST |url=https://www.ibtimes.co.in/bheeshma-movie-review-rating-by-audience-live-updates-813649 |title=Bheeshma movie review and rating by audience: Live updates, Nithiin and Rashmika Mandanna - IBTimes India |publisher=Ibtimes.co.in |date= |accessdate=2020-02-21}}</ref>\n\nAustralian Stars rated it 4/5 \"A great entertainer, The whole cast was amazing and Venky's movie is all the way a winner. This is your perfect weekend watch.\" ''[[Koimoi.com]]'' editor Rohit Mohan rated the film 3/5 and stated \"Nithiin comeback after one and half years is totally natural and a smash hit. The movie strikes right to the audience and [[Jishu Sengupta]] , Rashmika Mandanna did complete justice to their role.\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.koimoi.com/reviews/bheeshma-movie-review-nithiin-rashmika-mandanna-rom-com/ |title=Bheeshma Movie Review: Nithiin & Rashmika Mandanna's Rom-Com With A Strong 'Organic' Message Strikes The Right Chord |publisher=Koimoi.com |date= |accessdate=2020-02-21}}</ref> ''[[Times of India]]'' editor rated 3/5 star and stated \"If you loved Chalo, giving Bheeshma a chance is a no-brainer (pun intended). Just don\u2019t go expecting something even remotely sane or novel and you won\u2019t be disappointed.\" <ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/entertainment/telugu/movie-reviews/bheeshma/movie-review/74238190.cms |title=Bheeshma Movie Review {3/5}: Venky Kudumula doing what he does best |publisher=M.timesofindia.com |date= |accessdate=2020-02-21}}</ref>\n\n==Box Office==\nOverseas it collected<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.boxofficecollection2020.com/bheeshma-6-day-box-office-collection/ | title=Bheeshma Box Office Collection heading towards next Tollywood Hit| date=26 February 2020}}</ref> over $684,000 on its first weekend.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telugucinema.com/news/us-box-office-bheeshma-inching-towards-1-million|title=US Box Office Bheeshma Inching Towards 1 Million|work=telugucinema.com|access-date=24 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{IMDb title|tt11199356}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bheeshma Movie}}\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:Telugu-language films]]\n[[Category:2020s Telugu-language films]]\n[[Category:2020 films]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Hyderabad, India]]\n[[Category:Indian romantic comedy films]]\n[[Category:2020s romantic comedy films]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2020 Indian film directed by Venky Kudumula}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Bheeshma \n| image          = Bheeshma Poster.jpeg\n| caption        = Theatrical release poster\n| director       = Venky Kudumula\n| producer       = Suryadevara Naga Vamsi\n| writer         = Venky Kudumula\n| screenplay     = Venky Kudumula\n| story          = Venky Kudumula\n| starring       = {{ubl|[[Nithiin]]|[[Rashmika Mandanna]]|[[Anant Nag]]|[[Vennela Kishore]]}}\n| music          = Mahati Swara Sagar\n| cinematography = Sai Sriram\n| editing        = Navin Nooli\n| studio         = Sithara Entertainments\n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{Film date|df=yes|2020|2|21|ref1=<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/haarikahassine/status/1192299051003179008?s=19|title=Here's the f