ahlia (horse)|Dahlia]]\n* 1974: {{sic|hide=y|Mississipian}}\n* 1975: Anne's Pretender\n* 1976: [[Youth (horse)|Youth]]\n* 1977: [[Crystal Palace (horse)|Crystal Palace]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of French flat horse races]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n* [[France Galop]] / [[Racing Post]]:\n** {{France-Galop|1979|P|00872}}, {{France-Galop|1980|P|00864}}, {{France-Galop|1981|P|00816}}, {{France-Galop|1982|P|00855}}, {{France-Galop|1983|P|00869}}, {{France-Galop|1984|P|00862}}, {{France-Galop|1985|P|00849}}, {{France-Galop|1986|P|00879}}, {{France-Galop|1987|P|00852}}, {{France-Galop|1988|P|00892}}\n** {{France-Galop|1989|P|00926}}, {{Racing Post|102110|1990|09|16|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|106934|1991|09|15|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|111824|1992|09|13|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|116864|1993|09|12|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|122001|1994|09|11|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|127466|1995|09|10|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|230821|1996|09|15|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|243621|1997|09|14|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|257236|1998|09|13|211|longchamp}}\n** {{Racing Post|272484|1999|09|12|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|286958|2000|09|10|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|306715|2001|09|16|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|322562|2002|09|15|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|339136|2003|09|14|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|358649|2004|09|12|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|391827|2005|09|11|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|416727|2006|09|10|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|440970|2007|09|16|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|466284|2008|09|14|211|longchamp}}\n** {{Racing Post|491095|2009|09|13|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|514690|2010|09|12|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|539546|2011|09|11|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|564176|2012|09|16|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|587393|2013|09|15|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|610554|2014|09|14|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|635168|2015|09|13|211|longchamp}}, {{Racing Post|659004|2016|09|11|204|chantilly}}\n----\n* [ht