only appearing in the first four episodes.\n\n{{Episode table\n|background = #21476C\n|overall    = \n|title      = \n|director   = \n|writer     = \n|airdate    = \n|viewers    = \n|country    = UK\n|forceoverall = y\n|titleT     = Episode\n|viewersR   = <ref name=\"barb.co.uk\"/>\n|episodes   = \n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=57\n| Title=Episode 1\n| WrittenBy= [[Derren Litten]]\n| DirectedBy= [[Robin Shepperd]]\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2017|3|1|df=y}}\n|Viewers=5.79\n| ShortSummary= The Dawsons' holiday starts with a bang when Eddie has an accident and Sheron's fashion taste is put into question. An old inheritance puts a smile Kenneth's face. Meanwhile, Tiger and Joey are in a party mood as Sam, the new holiday rep and former guest at the Solana, takes them under her wing.\n\n'''First appearance of''' [[Kate Fitzgerald]] as Loretta Chase.<br />\n\n'''Absent:''' [[Johnny Vegas]] as Geoff Maltby, [[Elsie Kelly]] as Noreen Maltby, [[Janine Duvitski]] as [[Jacqueline Stewart (fiction)|Jacqueline Stewart]], [[Paul Bazely]] as Troy Ramsbottom and [[Selina Griffiths]] as Pauline Maltby.\n\n'''Return of''' [[Shelley Longworth]] as Sam Wood.<br />\n\n'''Guest Starring Jofre Alsina, [[Nigel Havers]] and Jonathan Hawkins\n| LineColor=21476C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=58\n| Title=Episode 2\n| WrittenBy= Derren Litten\n| DirectedBy= Robin Shepperd\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2017|3|8|df=y}}\n|Viewers=4.95\n| ShortSummary= Kenneth inadvertently starts up a mini-cab business whilst Joyce is asked to go to a conference in the city of [[Barcelona]], but panics when she finds out she has to deliver a speech in Spanish. Elsewhere, Sheron's mother Loretta arrives at the Solana to join the family on holiday, and it turns out she has already made quite an impression in Benidorm from the night before. Joey thinks he has managed to sign Tiger and himself up for a free trip to [[Ibiza]], but things do not go according to plan.\n\n'''Absent:''' [[Johnny Vegas]] as 